<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
   <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-9aIt2nRpC12Uk9gS9baDl411NQApFmC26EwAOH8WgZl5MYYxFfc+NcPb1dKGj7Sk" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <title>DearFemi</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <style type="text/css">
      a, a:visited, a:focus, a:hover {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="header">
      <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-success" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%;" aria-valuenow="100" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="jumbotron" style="text-align: center;">
        <u><%= link_to '_Dear Femi_', root_path, class: "display-3"%></u>
        <p class="lead">Let's think and talk with friends<br>about FEMINISM, GENDER, and your best life!</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p class="lead">
        <p>『Dear Femi（ディア フェミ）』は、みんなが良くなる方法をいっしょに考える憩いの場です。</p>
        <%= image_tag 'sdg_icon_wheel_2.png', size: "77x77", alt: "SDGsアイコン"%>&nbsp;&nbsp;<%= image_tag 'sdg_icon_05_ja_2.png', size: "77x77", alt: "SDGz5ジェンダー平等を実現しようアイコン"%>
      </div>
    </header>
    <%= yield %>
    <footer class="fixed-bottom">
      <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-success" role="progressbar" style="width: 100%;">Copyright&copy;2021 Femi Woke All Rights Reserved</div>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.0/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-OgVRvuATP1z7JjHLkuOU7Xw704+h835Lr+6QL9UvYjZE3Ipu6Tp75j7Bh/kR0JKI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>